Class OmlSearch

java.lang.Object
io.opencaesar.oml.util.OmlIndex
io.opencaesar.oml.util.OmlSearch
public final class OmlSearch extends OmlIndex
The Search API for the model. It complements the OmlIndex API by additional utilities.
